{"title":"Docker，WSL报错修复","uid":"cb7de42845102afdff079e63af1eb06a","slug":"Docker报错修复","date":"2023-10-31T01:32:06.000Z","updated":"2023-11-02T08:42:05.619Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Docker报错修复.json","keywords":null,"cover":"images/docker1.jpg","content":"<p>在我新加了一块硬盘之后，发现Docker报错无法打开，经排查后发现wsl安装不上，并报错：<a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/piKmUIA\"><img src=\"https://z1.ax1x.com/2023/11/02/piKmUIA.png\" alt=\"piKmUIA.png\"></a></p>\n<p>在尝试过包括重装，关闭可选虚拟化功能等方法后均无效，最后发现是VMware出了问题。</p>\n<p><strong>解决方法：</strong></p>\n<p>卸载VMware后重装，如果你和我一样把原来的盘给合并了，那么就先新增一个原来一样的盘符，如D:  </p>\n<p>打开磁盘管理-右键压缩卷-分配少一点空间（几个g）-继续-新建卷-新建一样的盘符-一直下一步。</p>\n<p>然后卸载VMware，此时再安装wsl2就可以成功了，如运行<strong>wsl –set-version Ubuntu-20.04 2</strong>，安装完成后docker也就能打开了</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"在我新加了一块硬盘之后，发现Docker报错无法打开，经排查后发现wsl安装不上，并报错： 在尝试过包括重装，关闭可选虚拟化功能等方法后均无效，最后发现是VMw...","permalink":"/post/Docker报错修复","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":274,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":3,"path":"api/tags/教程.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"SoldAllFruit","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"SZU/IC-Studying...","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/fruit-lxe","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"报错ModuleNotFoundError:No module named 'cv2' 的解决","uid":"95935909fd699b81ee206cd97bb1ed27","slug":"报错ModuleNotFoundError-No-module-named-cv2","date":"2023-11-02T07:46:02.000Z","updated":"2023-11-02T08:40:51.173Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/报错ModuleNotFoundError-No-module-named-cv2.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/cv2-1.jpg","text":"在运行py文件时，经常说缺少各种各样的库，如’ cv2’,’pytorch’。 **首先，检查自己是不是真的安装完了这些依赖包。 ** 可以先试着注释掉 imp...","permalink":"/post/报错ModuleNotFoundError-No-module-named-cv2","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":702,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"报错解决","slu